data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and space at 435 Kiley Drive. A lovingly maintained home, perfectly nestled on 3 fenced acres in the vibrant community of Hoschton. With over 4,000 square feet of finished space, this home offers ample room for living and entertaining. As you enter, this home welcomes you with a clean and inviting atmosphere, boasting fresh paint and newly carpeted bedrooms. The charming kitchen stands as the heart of the home, boasting spacious counters, ample natural light, and practical appliances that cater to all your culinary needs. The living room, highlighted by its vast space and beautiful fireplace, offers a cozy setting for memorable family moments. The bedrooms promise restful nights, with the master suite featuring a generous walk-in closet and spacious bathroom with a stunning, remodeled shower. Further enhancing the property's appeal is the full, finished basement with a separate entrance, providing additional living space or potential for a variety of uses, from an in-law suite, to a home theater or a massive playroom. Outdoor enthusiasts and hobbyists will appreciate the handy workshop and storage shed, ensuring space for projects and equipment is never an issue. This house, with its expansive grounds, thoughtful updates, and prime Hoschton location, presents a unique opportunity to own a piece of comfort and convenience. Call or text RU4 Homes Team for a private showing today! Move Up to Any One of Our Listings, We'll Buy Your Home for CASH!*
